text: Vladimír Plaček (29 May 1965 – 2 August 2018) was a Czech physician and politician. Plaček was a member of the ČSSD. Plaček served on the Senate from 2012 until his death on 2 August 2018. Plaček died on 2 August 2018 at the age of 53. == References == Category:1965 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Czech physicians Category:Czech politicians
